<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Password Reset - Walk to School</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f2f2f2;
        padding: 20px;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 5px;
        padding: 30px;
      }
      h1 {
        font-size: 24px;
        color: #333;
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
      p {
        font-size: 16px;
        color: #666;
      }
      a#reset-password-link {
        text-decoration: none;
        color: #fff;
        background-color: #4caf50;
        padding: 12px 25px;
        border-radius: 4px;
        font-size: 16px;
        display: inline-block;
        margin-top: 20px;
      }
      .footer {
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #999;
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 30px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Password Reset - Walk to School</h1>
      <p>Hi there,</p>
      <p>
        We received a request to reset your password for the Walk to School app.
        If you didn't request this, you can safely ignore this email.
      </p>
      <p>To reset your password, click the button below:</p>
      <a
        id="reset-password-link"
        href="<%= passwordResetLink %>"
        target="_blank"
        >Reset Your Password</a
      >
      <p>Thanks,</p>
      <p>The Walk to School Team</p>
      <div class="footer">Â© 2023 Walk to School Team. All rights reserved.</div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
